@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_bnllem(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.sin(wp.cos((tmp + 0.75 * v2 + 0.88)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.69)))
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = wp.exp(v2)
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.06) / (v1 + 0.47 * v0 + 0.61)) - v1)
    data[tid] = v0
